
# Nomad V1.0.0


New CMMS application

- Improve network performance to preserve resources
- Adapt to local issues
- Well informed to secure interventions
- Communicate better with our customers and consumers
- Lay the foundations for a network asset management offering


## Technologies

#### Frontend

- Ionic v7.0.2
- Angular v15.0.0
- Capacitor v5.0.0
- MapLibre v3.2.2
- angular-oauth2-oidc v15.0.1

#### Backend

- Spring Boot v6.0.4
- Swagger UI v4.15.5


## Installation

#### Frontend (Desktop)

- npm intall
- ionic serve -c local

#### Frontend (Mobile - apk)

- npm install
- ionic build
- npx cap sync (synchronize the www folder with the android project)
- npx cap open android (open android studio)

#### Backend

- Installation basic

Note : Swagger uri /api/gmao/swagger-ui.html

#### Keycloak local

 - command start : kc.bat start-dev --http-port 9191


#### Convention Nommage Angular
 - attribute$ => Subject, Observable
 - onFunction => Event action (click, output, observable)
 - setFunction => Setter value
 - getFunction => Getter value
 - isFunction/hasFunction => Function return a boolean
 - function => Basic function


